{"tid":2428860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那隨時用「連坐法」、「誅九族」對付港人","createTime":"2021-03-02T01:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T02:29:54.000Z","uid":113435,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d877afee5f35b936f71f149fa40795e9737f5e0f","tid":2428860,"uid":113435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:11:48.000Z","msg":"尋晚發夢（真係發夢），夢見被國安拉咗，國安威脅要我爆有份參與既手足出嚟，又話軟禁咗我父母，再唔講佢哋會被餓死，又話知我老母有心臟病，唔比藥佢食都得。<br />\n<br />\n我驚到傻咗，係咁大叫「習大大萬歲」和唱國歌，最後鳩up咗一堆唔關事既人既名出嚟，佢先放我走，點知出嚟個陣，醫院已經通知我老豆老母走咗"},{"pid":"3b792bbdd75fb453fef66306e62ebd1420186cdd","tid":2428860,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:24:45.000Z","msg":"唔出奇。需要走手足快D走"},{"pid":"1010c299727c7e7d7b67ab8a6c832baf9457f0f3","tid":2428860,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"認真，op應該上過前線，走，家人一齊走，求下你"},{"pid":"4b30da14bb35e067898d0ca4d65918a4ae87c018","tid":2428860,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:26:02.000Z","msg":"中共返回一窮二白境地"},{"pid":"d50e4c63ea6da6945d076e4f2bfa32876b2b0287","tid":2428860,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccca45169ed363b02da12387b2d28e813853d8f3","tid":2428860,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T02:29:54.000Z","msg":"支那實行一套將來一定係香港實行手"}]}